data.description: Welcome to this charming home, offering 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a warm and inviting atmosphere. The well-lit kitchen is equipped with generous counter space, stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and a convenient built-in desk. The primary bedroom suite is a retreat of its own, featuring double vanities, a separate shower, and soaking tub. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with well-proportioned layouts and ample closet space. An upstairs loft provides flexibility, perfect for a home office or versatile living space. Enjoy the convenience of an upstairs laundry area, adding a touch of practicality. Step outside to the private backyard, complete with a patio and pergola. In an ideal location, making it a perfect choice for those seeking a blend of comfort and accessibility.
